# Created      : 28 Dec 2022
# Updated      : 25 Feb 2026
# Comments     : base script Copyright (C) 2022 Kris Occhipinti https://filmsbykris.com
#              : Uses default editor ($EDITOR) to edit to-do list.
#              : Limit to-do list to 7 items to maintain proper formating.
# TODO (Rick)  :
